snippet.title: The Masters: Survival Trailer 2
snippet.description:
Available to wish list now on Steam!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1881210/The_Masters_Survival

Tana (Katana) is testing the new Virtual Proxy Simulation, which is going to be used for training, as she fights the evil creatures known as the Shadow Dwellers. All is not what it seems however as she dives deeper into the system and faces off against an old foe, Master Nether.

Download the alpha demo here:
https://royalflushstudioz230.itch.io/the-masters-survival

Buy merch:
https://www.redbubble.com/i/t-shirt/The-Masters-Survival-Design-1-by-Ace230/73005843.FB110

Royal Flush Studioz website:
royalflushstudioz.com/masterssurvival

Credits:
Created by: Matthew "Ace" Weldon

Voices that appear in the video:
Jude Weldon - Katana(Tana)
Master Nether - Michael Martin

Master Survival Theme composed by Big Jake:
https://soundcloud.com/real-big-jake?utm_source=clipboard&utm_medium=text&utm_campaign=social_sharing

Particle effects created by (via Epic Marketplace):
Dragon Motion 
DC Assets
Kakky
NadirVFX
Anil Koylu
#gaming #indiegame #hacknslash #kickstarter #topdowngame #unreal4 #themasters
